Netizen contribution
Tonight, Hu Chenfeng, the author of the previously popular 100 yuan purchasing power challenge video, told his experience in a live broadcast
In the original video, he asked a question at the end of the video: There are still many people in this society who earn less than 100 yuan a day, how do they live?
Then the video was deleted when it was played 60w, so he changed the ending to "Super like! We are so happy" and saved the video until it was played 160w before it was deleted.
He also talked about his Douyin account being restricted and blocked without reason, and he could not upload videos to Bilibili.
